## Prisma Query 패턴

### 1. select로 필요한 필드만 조회

```typescript
const poll = await prisma.poll.findUnique({
  where: { id: pollId },
  select: {
    id: true,
    title: true,
    description: true,
    createdAt: true,
  },
});
```

### 2. include로 관계 데이터 포함

```typescript
const poll = await prisma.poll.findUnique({
  where: { id: pollId },
  include: {
    creator: {
      select: {
        id: true,
        name: true,
      },
    },
    options: {
      select: {
        id: true,
        description: true,
      },
    },
  },
});
```

### 3. \_count로 개수 조회

```typescript
const poll = await prisma.poll.findUnique({
  where: { id: pollId },
  include: {
    _count: {
      select: {
        votes: true,
        likes: true,
      },
    },
  },
});
```

### 4. orderBy로 정렬

```typescript
const polls = await prisma.poll.findMany({
  where: { creatorId: userId },
  orderBy: {
    createdAt: "desc", // 최신순
  },
});
```

### 5. Promise.all로 병렬 조회

```typescript
const [pollsCreated, votesCount, likesCount] = await Promise.all([
  prisma.poll.count({ where: { creatorId: user.id } }),
  prisma.vote.count({ where: { userId: user.id } }),
  prisma.pollLike.count({ where: { userId: user.id } }),
]);
```

